    neo:source "Source document: COLLECTING GOLD DUST: Nurturing the Dhamma in Daily Living, Chapter: MEDITATING ALL THE TIME, paragraph number 9, sentence number 6 on page 33"^^xsd:string ;
    neo:text "We want to turn the momentum of the current mind completely around so that it is going in the direction of wholesome momentum rather than unwholesome momentum."^^xsd:string .

